# Generated Map Data Rule

- `src/data/mapData.ts` is generated output. Do not hand-edit it.
- If map shape or map thresholds change, update inputs (`*.pgm` / YAML) or `scripts/processMap.mjs`, then regenerate.
- Use `node scripts/processMap.mjs` from repo root to regenerate.
- Put generated-map changes in a separate commit from app logic when possible.
- Prefer editing `src/data/floorPlan.ts` for post-processing and runtime constants.
